description.desc: [마스터 레벨 : 20]\nIncreases the crossbow mastery and accuracy. It only applies when a crossbow is in hand.
description.name: Crossbow Mastery

description.desc: [마스터 레벨 : 30]\nStrikes an another, far deadlier blow following the initial attack with a given success rate. It works only when holding a crossbow.\nRequired Skill : #cAt least Level 3 on Crossbow Mastery#
description.name: Final Attack : Crossbow

description.desc: [마스터 레벨 : 20]\nUses HP and MP to temporarily boost up the attacking speed of the crossbow. It only works with a crossbow in hand.\nRequired Skill : #cAt least Level 5 on Crossbow Mastery#
description.name: Crossbow Booster

description.desc: [마스터 레벨 : 20]\nIncreases the success rate for pushing off the monsters when swinging a crossbow.  As the level rises, the number of monsters that one can push off with one swing increases.
description.name: Power Knock-Back

description.desc: [마스터 레벨 : 20]\nTemporarily allows the character to fire crossbow arrows without using up the arrows. Only works with a crossbow in hand.\nRequired Skill : #cAt least Level 5 on Bow Booster#
description.name: Soul Arrow : Crossbow

description.desc: [마스터 레벨 : 30]\nAttacks up to 6 monsters at once with a powerful arrow, which penetrates through them. Damage decreases as the arrow flies through.
description.name: Iron Arrow : Crossbow
